.SH NAME
bk getuser \- display user name
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bk getuser
.B [\-r]
.SH DESCRIPTION
This command displays \*(BK's idea of the caller's user name.
With the 
.B \-r
option, ignores
.IR $BK_USER .
